description:
Give your heroes some additional color! Why not start with a Contrast skin set?

This DLC unlocks a brand new set of skins for:
* Alice
* Medusa
* King Arthur
* Sinbad
* Beowulf
* Little Red

Check out our 80s-themed skins for Unmatched: Digital Edition as well!
name: Unmatched: Digital Edition - Contrast Skin Bundle 1
